hopobject.body: I work here slippery stuff gel uk We love how Kourtney has matched the floral print with her shorts, tapping into not one but two trends for summer. As Kourtney will be very aware, floral prints have been blooming all over the fashion world since designers like Dolce & Gabbana, Simone Rocha, Erdem and Chanel all sent models down their SS/13 catwalks in pretty blossoms. Whether oversized or ditzy, flowers have adorned dresses, skirts, coats and even trainers.
